#. type: Plain text
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:27
msgid ""
"This project is licensed under \\doclicenseLongNameRef.  It is community-"
"driven, and has a \\href{\\repourl}{GitHub repository}.  Everyone is welcome "
"to contribute, make changes, and fix errors.  You can get in touch with "
"creators through \\href{\\discordurl}{Discord} or by writing in the "
"\\href{\\bggthreadurl}{BoardGameGeek thread}."
msgstr ""
"本项目采用 \\doclicenseLongNameRef 授权。它由社区推动，并有一个 "
"\\href{\\repourl}{GitHub 仓库}。欢迎所有人贡献内容、提交修改并修正错误。你可"
"以通过 \\href{\\discordurl}{Discord} 联系创作者，也可以在 "
"\\href{\\bggthreadurl}{BoardGameGeek 帖子} 中留言。"

#. type: center
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:33
msgid ""
"\\textit{I’m doing this out of the love of learning games and wanting to "
"understand their complexities.}"
msgstr ""
"\\textit{我做这件事，是出于对学习游戏的热爱，也因为我想理解它们的复杂之处。}"

