#.  Source: https://heroes.thelazy.net/index.php/Restoration_of_Erathia_Manual_Page_84
#. type: Plain text
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:83
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Castle:} Human armies rallied under the banners of Clerics and "
"Knights, bolstered by the might of Griffins and protected by Angels."
msgstr ""
"\\textbf{城堡：} 人类军队在牧师与骑士的旗帜下集结，由狮鹫的强大力量支援，并受"
"到天使保护。"

#.  Source: https://heroes.thelazy.net/index.php/Restoration_of_Erathia_Manual_Page_88
#. type: Plain text
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:86
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Dungeon:} Subterranean forces led by Warlocks and Overlords, "
"wielding dark magic and bending fearsome creatures to their will."
msgstr ""
"\\textbf{地下城：} 由术士和领主率领的地下势力，施展黑暗魔法，并驱使可怖生物服"
"从他们的意志。"

#.  Source: https://heroes.thelazy.net/index.php/Restoration_of_Erathia_Manual_Page_100
#. type: Plain text
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:89
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Necropolis:} Legions of the undead, commanded by Necromancers and "
"Death Knights, who sap the strength of the living to fuel their own."
msgstr ""
"\\textbf{墓园：} 亡灵军团，由死灵法师和死亡骑士统领，他们汲取生者的力量以滋养"
"自身。"

#. type: Plain text
#: sections/title_with_toc.tex:91
msgid "More Factions, Heroes, and their armies await in the expansions."
msgstr "更多阵营、英雄和他们的军队将在扩展中登场。"
